Today was AWESOME! Of course it's snowing but we had 2 chorus practices during school. One at recess and one at 1:50. Me,Lauren,Kate,Emily,Chrissy,Ashlea A,Ashley B and Julie B were singing with A LOT of excitment but we almost got in trouble cuz we sang a lil bit too loud haha. Anways, I only had 1 thing for homework but had to research some stuff 4 a project. I shoveled some snow and stayed out there and made a fort but it was tiny. I went online and talked for a bit. I was talkin to my brother's friend Joey and he said the next time we have a snowball fight, IM him to come over and he'll be on mine,my bros and my 2 neighbors  team cuz last time I had a snowball fight, I got hit in the face and he felt bad for me. OMG!!!! I wanna have a snowball fight soo badly. It's gonna snow A LOT this week so I'm hoping this weeek , we can have the snowball fight. I ate dinner then went back online. Just hangin round the house right now. My mom made cookies and I'm gonna eat sum soon. I can't wait!!!!Tomorrow is our concert and I'm in band and chorus. Well I'm gonna watch tv, go online, and go to bed sumtime.

Love,Rebecca <33 I  LOVE SNOW <33333333333

Sorry I haven't but updating but also for another reason is that LJ had a huge power failure but now it's back up and running again. Today, I went to the city and saw a show called "Cookin". It was cool and funny. For dinner, we ate at a chinese restaurant and the food there was really good. We also went in a few other stores. Then, we went to the bakery and I got hot chocolate and something else I don't remember but I know it was good  lol. My brother got a deck of cards so we played "Spit" and 5 card poker. It was fun. We got home about 21 minutes ago. Last night I watched the Jets vs the  Steelers game and unfortunately, the Jets lost. NOOOO!!!! I'm very disappointed in them lol. I hope the Steelers lose the next game lol. Anyway, I went to my friend Shannon M's house and came back around 2:00 AM. We watched "The Village" and it wasn't even scary. We played with their pet ferret Rascal. He's sooooooo cute. I watched a lil bit of tv when I got home and then finally fell asleep. Well, I think I'm gonna do stuff online, play games, watch tv and then finally at sometime, go to sleep.

 

Love,Rebecca <3

My other LJ account is LessThanJake345 but now I changed it and this is my new one. Today, we had school until 3 as always. OMG! We had a substitute teacher. It wasn't so bad. After school, I came home and did homework and went online for a bit. For dinner, I had popcorn chicken with 2 other stuff. It was so yummy especially the chicken. Tomorrow after school, I have chorus and in the morning I have band. Today, I had Yearbook in the morning and we did a lot of work and emmers got sick so I hope she's in school tomorrow. Softball starts on APRIL 16th!!!! I CAN'T WAIT! I WANT IT TO START lol. Sorry I went a little too crazy there. Ok maybe not a little, maybe a lot. I might be doing the softball clinic. I'm sooooo bored right now. I have no clue of wut to do. I've been SO CRAZY today. I was talking on the phone with Kate and Lauren before and just talking bout stuff. So..... I guess I'm gonna go now.

 

Love,Rebecca <33

Feel Better Emmers <333333333
